1
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,119
Don't worry, Manager Xie.

2
00:00:41,399 --> 00:00:43,280
I've already tipped off the security team.

3
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:44,960
The moment they throw a punch,

4
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,880
they'll be hauled straight to the police.

5
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,280
Once Zhu Yihai gets into a fight,

6
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,840
it won't be just a 15-day sentence.

7
00:00:50,359 --> 00:00:53,119
So someone told you

8
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:55,479
that I'm the one who ruined Dongxing Factory?

9
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,079
That's right.

10
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:58,880
Damn it!

11
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:03,640
Bring it on!

12
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,319
Stop!

13
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,239
Bro.

14
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,079
Stop it!

15
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,120
Stop just 'cause you said so?

16
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,280
Get out of here, now!

17
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:14,879
What kind of talk is that?

18
00:01:14,879 --> 00:01:16,879
There's no way we're leaving you behind.

19
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,120
Absolutely not.

20
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,760
Then we'll all end up dead here.

21
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,799
You think you can get away?

22
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,000
None of you are getting out alive.

23
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,000
Get 'em!

24
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,560
A fight's breaking out!

25
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:30,560
They're fighting!

26
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,439
Brothers,

27
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,319
charge!

28
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,040
Listen up, all of you!

29
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:41,040
I'm Guohong Steel Plant Chief of Security,

30
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,200
Dao Balian.

31
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,319
Drop your weapons

32
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,760
and become

33
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,799
Drop them!

34
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:47,920
A fight's broken out, bro!

35
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,680
They're fighting!

36
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,359
Surrender your weapons!

37
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:52,359
There's a fight, bro!

38
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:54,079
You're all surrounded!

39
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:54,879
Did a fight break out?

40
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,239
Face the punishment of the law!

41
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,200
Disturbing public order

42
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,640
is an unforgivable crime.

43
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:00,760
I,

44
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,959
Chief of Security Dao Balian,

45
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,319
on behalf of the factory and the people,

46
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:07,159
will bring you to justice!

47
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,879
Beautifully said!

48
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,159
Thanks for your hard work.

49
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:17,120
Never take a thing from the people.

50
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:17,960
Hello.

51
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:19,080
Manager Xie.

52
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,199
Hello.

53
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,680
Chief Dao, I was right, wasn't I?

54
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,759
This bunch is nothing but trouble.

55
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:26,000
And now they're mob brawling.

56
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,280
Lucky you arrived just in time.

57
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,520
Ridding the people of a menace!

58
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:30,919
Isn't that right?

59
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:31,840
Yeah.

60
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,280
Come on, let me take a look.

61
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,120
Ridding what menace?

62
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,240
We're getting rid of you lot,

63
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,560
you mob brawlers!

64
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,400
What menace?

65
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,599
Is watching Dragon Ball a crime now?

66
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,719
Manager Xie.

67
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:57,000
This is who's disturbing public order?

68
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,479
Guess the old man won't do time this round.

69
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,280
Hurry up.

70
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,719
What the hell are you doing?

71
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:03,319
Get over there.

72
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,479
Damn, you're pretty good.

73
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,360
Of course.

74
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:11,080
Bro, I brought him for you.

75
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,680
Go ahead and ask.

76
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:13,879
You little fatso.

77
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:16,199
Said Zhu Yihai is Giant Wood Group's #2?

78
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,280
That was me.

79
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:18,919
Then who tricked our factory director,

80
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,879
sold the land and embezzled the funds?

81
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:21,919
It was him.

82
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,840
Can you tell the truth?

83
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,919
Even if you beat me to death, it's you.

84
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:28,360
Who said I'd beat you to death?

85
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:32,560
What are you gonna do?

86
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,479
Buddy.

87
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,599
You've got dark circles under your eyes.

88
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,520
Let me give your kidneys a boost.

89
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,719
Looks like your brain's not working right.

90
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,599
Let me fix that heart of yours.

91
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:46,639
Talk.

92
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,319
Xie... Xie Fan.

93
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,759
Xie Fan is the real number two.

94
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,360
Xie Fan.

95
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,840
Well, well.

96
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,439
Using others to do your dirty work.

97
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,360
Counting on Long Xiao backing you up,

98
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,120
you dumped all the filth onto me.

99
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,400
You're pretty damn sly.

100
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,879
Back then you bullied me every which way.

101
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,599
Now your day has finally come.

102
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,159
Manager Xie.

103
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:14,159
So the one disturbing public order

104
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:14,960
is you.

105
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,800
Come with me.

106
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,639
Let go!

107
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,040
What the hell?

108
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,439
What the hell?

109
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,519
I'd like to see who dares touch me today.

110
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,040
Who dares cross the Giant Wood Group?

111
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:40,439
Using others' power to act tough, Xie Fan!

112
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,959
Bro, listen to me.

113
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,160
I've told you before.

114
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,279
Ambition is a good thing,

115
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:59,800
but you'd better weigh the consequences.

116
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,439
Today, in front of all these people,

117
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,720
I'm gonna say it again.

118
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,959
Giant Wood Group

119
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,560
has only one second-in-command,

120
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,120
and that's Zhu Yihai.

121
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:11,839
Xie Fan,

122
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,600
from this moment on,

123
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,120
in Giant Wood Group,

124
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,639
you're nothing.

125
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,720
Get the hell out.

126
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,519
I'm not leaving.

127
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,079
I won't go. What did I do wrong?

128
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,279
Why treat me like this?

129
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:27,639
I'm taking this knife back as evidence.

130
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,720
Family matters

131
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,000
should be handled internally.

132
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:30,920
Let's go.

133
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,920
Move.

134
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,519
Brother Yihai,

135
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,079
about Xie Fan,

136
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,079
I owe you an apology.

137
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,639
Yeah.

138
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,560
What's all this commotion

139
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,439
you're making today?

140
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,759
It's fine, bro.

141
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,600
You're really something,

142
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,560
Zhu Yihai.

143
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:54,920
Got some real skills now, huh?

144
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,360
Of course. If my bro had no skills,

145
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,680
how could he open a foot massage parlor?

146
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:01,399
Brother Yihai, you're opening

147
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,399
a foot massage parlor?

148
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,519
That's right.

149
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:05,680
A foot parlor sounds good and all,

150
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,800
but around here,

151
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,240
the girls are pretty hard to find.

152
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,879
Why would we need girls?

153
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:12,839
If not girls,

154
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,519
then who?

155
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,360
Brother Yihai,

156
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,279
you really know how to party.

157
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,600
Don't worry.

158
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,000
About this foot parlor business,

159
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,040
I fully support you.

160
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,839
Consider it my apology.

161
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,240
I'll be heading off now.

162
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,720
I'll leave you to it.

163
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:33,399
I'm off.

164
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:34,439
Take care, Boss Long.

165
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,519
Nice car.

166
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:38,319
So annoying.

167
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:40,800
Now that's settled,

168
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,879
let's talk about us.

169
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,399
Us? Us?

170
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,040
Sis-in-law, let's talk back home.

171
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,639
Yeah, back home.

172
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:48,040
Who're you calling sis-in-law?

173
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,839
Push the cart.

174
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,360
Why is it just you two?

175
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,079
Is Dahai hurt?

176
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:05,040
No, Brother Hai's parking out back.

177
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,920
Parking.

178
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,480
Top up 100, get 100 free.

179
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,759
Members get a Dragon Ball comic free.

180
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:17,000
Are we even making money?

181
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:19,040
Don't ask me, it's all Dahai's idea.

182
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:21,480
Brother Hai did time and now

183
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,839
his brain's getting dumber and dumber.

184
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,120
Real genius, you.

185
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,560
Even if Dahai really lost his mind,

186
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,839
he'd still be sharper than you.

187
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,800
Otherwise, why would Sis fall for him?

188
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,720
Exactly.

189
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:35,600
Sis, Sis...

190
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,759
Which "Sis" do you mean?

191
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,000
I'm sorry!

192
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:41,560
You're back, Brother Hai.

193
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,360
Qian Huilian, what are you doing here?

194
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:45,720
Qiao Lili.

195
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,519
If I'm not mistaken,

196
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:50,000
I'm the one who funded this pool hall.

197
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,279
Do I need a reason to visit my own shop?

198
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,759
Sis, have a drink.

199
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,160
Dahai, are you okay?

200
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:56,879
I'm totally fine.

201
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,639
On a Saturday,

202
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,319
instead of running your business,

203
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:02,120
you go off brawling?

204
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:08,199
Top up 100, get 100 free.

205
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,720
Members get a Dragon Ball comic free.

206
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,279
Not bad.

207
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,639
Quite the business mind you've got.

208
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,279
Zhu Yihai.

209
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,879
When do you plan to pay me back?

210
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:22,800
I owe her money?

211
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,480
Got any proof?

212
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,879
Sure do.

213
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:37,039
Our Dahai's Giant Wood Group's #2 now.

214
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,080
You think he really can't pay you back?

215
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,960
So, dear #2 of Giant Wood Group,

216
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,960
when are you paying me back?

217
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:48,399
Money, money, money.

218
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,120
You really live up to your surname.

219
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,679
Once Dahai gets Aimin Street,

220
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:54,399
who'd care about your dinky pool hall?

221
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,440
Are you serious?

222
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,519
Yeah.

223
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,639
After Aimin Street is demolished...

224
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,840
Alright, Zhu Yihai.

225
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,279
See you next Saturday, then.

226
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,919
If I don't see that 67,000 yuan,

227
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,120
this pool hall

228
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,320
will be taking my surname.

229
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,480
Qian Huilian, kicking me while I'm down!

230
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:12,000
Didn't you say you didn't care about it?

231
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,480
See you next Saturday.

232
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,480
Sis, Sis...

233
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,000
You won't even let me speak.

234
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,919
It's all a misunderstanding!

235
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,919
Yeah, yeah.

236
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,159
Don't mind him.

237
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,000
This is the real Sis we know.

238
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,799
Glad you know.

239
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:26,759
We know your bark's worse than your bite.

240
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:29,519
You want Dahai to succeed the most.

241
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:31,039
And you care about him the most.

242
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,559
Who cares about him?

243
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:33,720
Why would I bother?

244
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,039
Don't mind him.

245
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:39,600
Boss Long.

246
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,879
Name your price.

247
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,039
Five million.

248
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,720
Five million?

249
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,639
I want all of Aimin Street.

250
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,559
I know plenty of folks at the plant

251
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:53,399
can't even put food on the table now.

252
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,279
If this money goes to them,

253
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,720
it'd let them

254
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,399
get through the winter, right?

255
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,600
Boss Long,

256
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,000
you're a real stand-up guy.

257
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:06,799
But to give my workers a good year,

258
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,519
maybe

259
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,240
we need a bit more.

260
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,559
You tell me, Factory Director Ge.

261
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:13,879
How much more?

262
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,360
Ten million.

263
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:22,440
Twenty million, take it or leave it.

264
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,240
Boss Long,

265
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,720
twelve million.

266
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,000
Factory Director Ge,

267
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,159
I think

268
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:35,519
you could take a smaller cut yourself.

269
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,639
We leaders,

270
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:39,399
we don't think of ourselves.

271
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,639
We have to look out for our workers, right?

272
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:43,440
Right?
